text: Like <@U016BDEQ40J> said. I put the work into blocks and be realistic about what projects I can do in that time block. So I like to time myself because it makes it fun and challenging. However, it can get a bit stressful too. I start with 30 minute time blocks and for some projects 1 hour time blocks and I break 5 minutes in between. Something also to remember is to use that airplane mode while doing this. Hope that helps.
